          "content": {
            "body": "The personal portfolio and engineering showcase of **Michael Douglas**. Built on DDS v3 — the original universal renderer that powers this entire ecosystem. The proof that one person with the right architecture can ship 16 production sites from a single monorepo."
          },
          "display": { "layout": "text-only" }
