        {
          "id": "tech",
          "type": "section",
          "name": "tech",
          "subject": { "title": "The Technology" },
          "content": {
            "body": "Every site is powered by the **DDS Universal Renderer** — a config-driven section rendering system where entire pages are expressed as JSON. One shared renderer package. 28+ section types. 9 theme variants. Infinite configurations.\n\nThe monorepo uses **pnpm workspaces + Turborepo** for build orchestration. The renderer is a **git submodule** maintained independently. Each app is a **Next.js 14** project that can be extracted and sold as a standalone product.\n\nOpen source packages selected for each vertical: **Medusa.js** (commerce), **Fumadocs** (docs), **Keystatic** (content), **Recharts** (dashboards), **Scalar** (API docs), **Sandpack** (playgrounds), **GSAP + Lenis** (animation), **Supabase** (realtime)."
          },
          "display": { "layout": "text-only" }
        },
